Gadgetbahn is [[pejorative]] term used by some [http://www.publictransit.us/PublicTransitUS.php?catid=20&blogid=8 transit professionals] to describe what they view as infeasible transportation concepts.

Perhaps the most well-known transportation concept to be labled gadgetbahn is [[Personal Rapid Transit]] or PRT.

